  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Immunologic parameters</measure>
    <time_frame>7 days</time_frame>
    <description>Blood level of the following parameters on preoperative, postoperative day 1, 3, 5-7.
IL-1beta, IL-1ra, IL-2, IL-4, IL-5, IL-6, Il-7, IL-8, Il-9, Il-10, Il-12, Il-13, IL-15, Il-17,basic FGF (Fibroblast growth factors).
Cell Analytics - (mononuclear) T-Cells incl. killer cells, CD2, CD3, CD4, CD8, CD25, CD30, CD19, CD20, CD138, CD56, CD56, CD303, CD304, NK cytotoxicity (non-radioisotope), CTL cytotoxicity (non-radioisotope), T cell proliferation, B cell, T cell.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
